          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1597159462710-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1597159462710-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1597159462710-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> pepper strips </strong>and <strong>courgette rounds </strong>to a baking tray (or two!) with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give it a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15-20 min or until everything is cooked through and tender – this is your <strong>roasted veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1597159471438-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1597159471438-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
