        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>spiced chicken</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until golden</p><p>Add a couple of splashes of <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> to the pan and cover with a lid</p><p>Cook for a further 10-12 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1597159506059-x200.jpg",
