            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems, then chop them finely and discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add most<strong> </strong>of the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and <strong>mint </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) to the <strong>cooked bulgur wheat</strong> and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>herby bulgur</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1597159517465-x200.jpg",
