            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>cooked spiced chicken</strong> finely and serve with the <strong>herby bulgur</strong>, <strong>roasted veg</strong> and <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>warm harissa dressing</strong> all over</p><p>Garnish with your<strong> toasted flaked almonds</strong> and a<strong> lemon wedge</strong>,<strong> </strong>then<strong> </strong>sprinkle over the <strong>remaining chopped parsley </strong>and <strong>mint</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
